item.title: Apache
item.description: APACHE In the last days of the course, I will try to convey the web topic told by our climax teacher. Doruk Hodja explained the subject on the slide. He then gave us some tasks and asked us to do them. I plan to tell what I have left in my mind from my own notes and teacher. If you see anything wrong, please do not forget to report it.
